{"word":"ἐπαισθάνομαι","slug":"ἐπαισθάνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαισθάνομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-αισθήσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-ῃσθόμην</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to have a perception</i> or <i>feeling of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to perceive, hear</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}